The counterplay to zed is to counter pick him. Hell you can play most ad bruisers midlane and they completely smash him zero problems. {{champion:48}} {{champion:23}} {{champion:266}} (which will likely LOWER your chance to win the game unless you have an ap top)

The fact is he is an assassin that counters mages played in mid where everyone plays mages hoping to beat him.

Only "mages" that can avoid his ult in some way can actually stand a chance.{{champion:105}} {{champion:8}}
